{"tid":1846631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無方法建立只有香港人既醫院？","createTime":"2020-01-27T16:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T16:38:20.000Z","uid":173333,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"760f9fe4199cf117b2e7590039ec7ac25110438d","tid":1846631,"uid":173333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:38:20.000Z","msg":"FF發夢一下 <br />\n香港自願慰隊負責守衛只限本港住滿7年既市民進出醫院. 令到真正本地香港人可以得到應有既醫療服務.因為只要社區爆發，醫療系統會立即進入停擺，令好多長期病患者同急症得唔到治療而死亡.<br />\n同時建議把禮賓府同政總分別改為病毒研究同收容所，劃出林病既住所做臨時停屍間. <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}